# Offline UPI Mesh Simulation System

## 🚀 Overview
This project simulates offline transaction propagation using mesh networking and delayed backend processing.

## ⚙️ Tech Stack
- Java (Spring Boot)
- Maven
- H2 Database

## ▶️ How it works
1. Inject transaction
2. Gossip propagation
3. Bridge to backend

## 🌐 Run
mvnw.cmd spring-boot:run  
http://localhost:8081

## ⚠️ Note
This is a simulation, not a real payment system.
